### Get available delivery boys
GET http://localhost:8000/api/dispatch/available-delivery-boys

### Assign delivery boy to order
POST http://localhost:8000/api/dispatch/assign/PASTE_ORDER_ID_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "deliveryBoyId": "PASTE_DELIVERY_BOY_ID_HERE",
    "distanceInKm": 4.5
}

### Get all dispatches
GET http://localhost:8000/api/dispatch

### Get dispatch by dispatch id
GET http://localhost:8000/api/dispatch/PASTE_DISPATCH_ID_HERE

### Get dispatch by order id
GET http://localhost:8000/api/dispatch/order/PASTE_ORDER_ID_HERE

### Update dispatch status
PUT http://localhost:8000/api/dispatch/PASTE_DISPATCH_ID_HERE/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "status": "dispatched"
}

### Mark dispatch delivered
PUT http://localhost:8000/api/dispatch/PASTE_DISPATCH_ID_HERE/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "status": "delivered"
}